{"tid":2281661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大學保衞戰一周年︱中大理大戰火留痕 油漆遮不掉義憤 燻黑裂痕留住圍城烽火","createTime":"2020-11-11T10:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T15:18:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"bc04418ed12179e2686e75f35bbacd7872eb8dd5","tid":2281661,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p-uEjUSGeT-hdtybLG4MyGn_wKY=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KJXZYQC2WZBUNL2TVXS5O4MIVQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp-uEjUSGeT-hdtybLG4MyGn_wKY%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKJXZYQC2WZBUNL2TVXS5O4MIVQ.JPG&h=85869853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中大&mdash;&mdash;鐵網圍橋 油漆遮不掉義憤<br />\n中大正門的民主女神像，頸上至今仍掛住一個豬嘴（防毒面罩），提醒學生去年11月中大遭警方狂射逾千枚催淚彈。前中大學生會會長蘇浚鋒說，雕像之前還給戴了頭盔，掛上「五大訴求，缺一不可」的牌子，他估計可能因為風吹雨打，或者已被校方移除。<br />\n<br />\n去年11月12日，示威者死守中大二號橋，在此將雜物扔下吐露港公路，試圖癱瘓由新界出九龍的交通，並以汽油彈抵抗警方催淚彈及水炮狂轟，「戰役」過後，橋面留下燒焦痕迹，更亭被焚毀。今年4月底，二號橋重開，橋身安裝了四米高倒鈎鐵絲網，以防有人再擲物到橋下，但走在其中猶如置身囚牢。記者10月底再訪時，橋上放置了一個全新更亭，也增加了兩名保安員駐守。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8PQN_UmeyEvq4CgbegI8-e_J7CA=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PEQWCKMC5RG3TB6DOOYB4SKWEU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8PQN_UmeyEvq4CgbegI8-e_J7CA%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPEQWCKMC5RG3TB6DOOYB4SKWEU.JPG&h=b79d11e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理大去年11月17日上午起成為主要戰場，至18日清晨，有速龍嘗試從A Core直衝入校園正門，示威者不斷在長樓梯拋擲和燃燒雜物，現場傳出多次爆炸聲響。如今，A Core長樓梯、尖東橋的天花板和地面仍可見明顯的煙燻痕迹。<br />\n<br />\n理大A Core長樓梯、尖東橋的天花板和地面仍可見明顯的煙燻痕迹。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201111/ZBYYQ4XT5RE5HHOA4S5R44Y344/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201111%2FZBYYQ4XT5RE5HHOA4S5R44Y344%2F&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=c26214ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201111%2FZBYYQ4XT5RE5HHOA4S5R44Y344%2F&h=31856748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201111/ZBYYQ4XT5RE5HHOA4S5R44Y344/</a>"},{"pid":"39bdfca77b975ef234877330d54d4dc711d7e70e","tid":2281661,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63db1546ed350884b8fd0234932b8c8c0cd82071","tid":2281661,"uid":362346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"不敢忘記"},{"pid":"ab72a44615e0364cef085faad35f4b79112b5998","tid":2281661,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39bdfca77b975ef234877330d54d4dc711d7e70e","tid":2281661,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:14:30.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"8e3f5276f109604e34662222a2a98cf5b47c0c2e","tid":2281661,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db0183e80c62d63b789c715aadc59536de3d37b","tid":2281661,"uid":276469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\